Ing '''Bulandu''', '''Bulan''' o '''Bugsuk''', a ''Vitiligo'' king Ingles, metung yang pangmaluatan (''chronic'') a sakit a mágdalang pangalako ning kule da reng dake ning [[balat]]. Maliliari iti neng deng [[melanocyte]], deng cell a mamie king [[:en:Human skin color|kule ning balat]] a manibat king [[neural crest]], mamamate la o e la gagana. Complicadu ing exactong sangkan ning bulandu, at e ra pa lubus a aintindian. Ating katibayan a tuturu king pamiabe-abe da reng sangkan a [[:en:Autoimmunity|autoimmune]], [[:en:Genetics|genetic]] o puli, ampong [[pangkapadurutan]] (''environmental''). Maralas ya muring mayayakit kareng taung ating diferencia king karelang [[thyroid]]. Kulang king metung a porciento ing pangapaliari na king king populasion king mabilug a yatu.<ref name=pmid7977362>{{cite journal |author=Nath SK, Majumder PP, Nordlund JJ |title=Genetic epidemiology of vitiligo: multilocus recessivity cross-validated |journal=American Journal of Human Genetics |volume=55 |issue=5 |pages=981–90 |year=1994 |month=November |pmid=7977362 |pmc=1918341}}</ref> Mas makelatan ya ing ''non-segmental'' a bulandu kesa kareng aliwang uri ning sakit a iti.

